{
    "chapter": 56,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "56:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>不可避免的复活日来临时，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "56:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>任何人都无法像今世那样对其予以否认。</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "56:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，悖逆的不信道将被投进火狱而降级，敬畏的信士被请进乐园而升级。</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "56:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当大地剧烈震动的时候，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "56:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>山脉被化为齑粉，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "56:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>粉末化为灰尘漫天飞舞。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "56:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那日，你们被分为三类，</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "56:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>用右手接取自己功过薄的幸运者，他们的地位真高大！</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "56:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>用左手接取自己功过薄的厄运者，他们的地位真卑劣！</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "56:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在今世最先行善者，在后世，他们将最先进入乐园。</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "56:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们是临近真主的，</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "56:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>是在恩泽的乐园里享受各种恩惠的，</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "56:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们是这个民众及古代众多民众中的部分人</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "56:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>和末日时刻的少部分人，他们是先行者和临近者。</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "56:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们坐在金丝编制的床榻上，</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "56:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们倚靠在这些床榻上，相对而坐，任何人都不会看到他人的后颈。</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "56:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有长生不老的仆人，轮流为他们服务，</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "56:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>仆人捧着永不间断的醴泉，往返于他们之间，</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "56:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那醴泉与今世的酒不同，不会使饮者眩晕，或因酩酊大醉而失去理智。</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "56:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>这些仆人捧着水果供他们挑选，</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "56:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以及他们喜好的鸟肉在他们中穿梭。</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "56:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在乐园里，他们享有明眸善睐的女子，</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "56:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>她们似藏于贝壳里的珍珠。</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "56:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那是对他们在今世所行善功的奖赏。</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "56:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们在乐园里听不到恶言和谎言，</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "56:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>听到的只是众天使对他们的平安祝福，以及他们相互间的祝福。</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "56:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>幸运者！幸运者是何等人呢？在真主那里，他们的地位和境况真尊贵！</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "56:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们享有无害的、没有刺的滨枣树，</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "56:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>硕果累累的香蕉树，</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "56:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>永不消逝的漫漫树荫，</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "56:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>川流不息的河水，</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "56:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>数之不尽的水果，</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "56:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>水果不会罄竭，无所谓季节，他们都可以随心所欲地采摘。</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "56:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>床榻上排放着被高高升起的褥，</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "56:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我确已把她们重塑成你们不曾见过的，</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "56:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>从未被任何人触摸过的处女，</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "56:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>她们年龄相仿、依恋丈夫，</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "56:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我为幸运的人创造了她们，作为幸运者的标志。</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "56:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们是之前众先知民众中的一部分人，</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "56:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以及最后的民众，即穆罕默德（愿主福安之）民众的一部分人。</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "56:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>厄运者！厄运者是何等人呢？他们的状态和归宿真恶劣！</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "56:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们处在毒风和沸水中，</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "56:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在黑烟的阴影下，</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "56:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那风既不凉爽，也不美观。</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "56:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在今世他们曾是享受的，他们唯一追求的只是自身的欲望。</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "56:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们曾执拗于不信真主及舍真主而崇拜偶像。</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "56:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们曾否认复活，并认为其是不可思议的，故嘲笑说：“难道我们死去，变成尘埃和腐骨后会被复生？</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "56:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以及我们早已逝去的先辈们也会被复活吗？”</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "56:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你对这些否认复活的人说：“人类古代的前人和后代的后人，</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "56:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>必将在复活日被集合以作清算和报酬。”</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "56:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>否认复活的人们啊！你们是迷失于端庄道路者，</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "56:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在复活日，将吃那攒楛木树的果实，那是最恶劣、最阴毒的果实。</p>"
        },
        "53": {
            "verses": {
                "56:53": {
                    "id": 53
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们靠那苦涩树的果实填充他们的空腹。</p>"
        },
        "54": {
            "verses": {
                "56:54": {
                    "id": 54
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>此外，他们需饮那滚烫的沸水，</p>"
        },
        "55": {
            "verses": {
                "56:55": {
                    "id": 55
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>如同患有消渴病的骆驼痛饮凉水一样。</p>"
        },
        "56": {
            "verses": {
                "56:56": {
                    "id": 56
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>上述的劣食和沸水，是惩罚日给予你们的款待。</p>"
        },
        "57": {
            "verses": {
                "56:57": {
                    "id": 57
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>否认复活的人们啊！我确已创造了你们，之前你们并不存在的，难道你们不信我会在死后复生你们吗？</p>"
        },
        "58": {
            "verses": {
                "56:58": {
                    "id": 58
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！难道你们不记得妻室的子宫里的精液吗？</p>"
        },
        "59": {
            "verses": {
                "56:59": {
                    "id": 59
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>把那精液造成人的是你们？还是我呢？</p>"
        },
        "60": {
            "verses": {
                "56:60": {
                    "id": 60
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我预定了你们的死亡，任何人都有一个不得提前也不能推后的定期，对于此事，我确是万能的。</p>"
        },
        "61": {
            "verses": {
                "56:61": {
                    "id": 61
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我有能力改变所知的你们的品性和状态，把你们创造成你们所不知道的品性和状态，</p>"
        },
        "62": {
            "verses": {
                "56:62": {
                    "id": 62
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们已经知道了我是怎样使你们初次被造，能初次创造你们的，当然也能在你们死后复活你们，难道你们不觉悟吗？</p>"
        },
        "63": {
            "verses": {
                "56:63": {
                    "id": 63
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你们没有看到你们在大地上耕种的种子吗？</p>"
        },
        "64": {
            "verses": {
                "56:64": {
                    "id": 64
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使这些种子生根发芽的，是你们呢？还是我呢？</p>"
        },
        "65": {
            "verses": {
                "56:65": {
                    "id": 65
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>假如我欲使那些庄稼成为枯木，我必使然，而你们则对此诧异。</p>"
        },
        "66": {
            "verses": {
                "56:66": {
                    "id": 66
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们说：“我们损失了我们的付出，我们是被惩罚的，</p>"
        },
        "67": {
            "verses": {
                "56:67": {
                    "id": 67
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>是被剥夺给养的。”</p>"
        },
        "68": {
            "verses": {
                "56:68": {
                    "id": 68
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你们没有看到你们所饮的水吗？</p>"
        },
        "69": {
            "verses": {
                "56:69": {
                    "id": 69
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使云中降下雨水的，是你们？还是我呢？</p>"
        },
        "70": {
            "verses": {
                "56:70": {
                    "id": 70
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>假如我欲使那水成为极咸的，不能饮用也不能灌溉，我必使然，如果你们不感谢真主怜悯而为你们降下甘甜的水的话。</p>"
        },
        "71": {
            "verses": {
                "56:71": {
                    "id": 71
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道你们没有看到你们因钻木而生的火吗？</p>"
        },
        "72": {
            "verses": {
                "56:72": {
                    "id": 72
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>创造了生火的树木的，是你们呢？还是我为厚待你们而创造的呢？</p>"
        },
        "73": {
            "verses": {
                "56:73": {
                    "id": 73
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我使这火成为你们后世的训诫，并使它成为旅途中的慰藉。</p>"
        },
        "74": {
            "verses": {
                "56:74": {
                    "id": 74
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当赞颂你伟大的主，祂远超越所有不符合祂的描述。</p>"
        },
        "75": {
            "verses": {
                "56:75": {
                    "id": 75
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以星辰的地方和位置盟誓！</p>"
        },
        "76": {
            "verses": {
                "56:76": {
                    "id": 76
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以这些位置盟誓是重大的，假如你们知道这盟誓的重大，其中有很多数不尽的迹象和借鉴。</p>"
        },
        "77": {
            "verses": {
                "56:77": {
                    "id": 77
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！向你们宣读的《古兰经》是尊贵的，其中有诸多伟大的益处。</p>"
        },
        "78": {
            "verses": {
                "56:78": {
                    "id": 78
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>它被记录于被保护的天牌上，</p>"
        },
        "79": {
            "verses": {
                "56:79": {
                    "id": 79
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>只有毫无罪过和过失的纯洁天使可触摸它，</p>"
        },
        "80": {
            "verses": {
                "56:80": {
                    "id": 80
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>它是由万物的创造者降示给祂的先知穆罕默德（愿主福安之）的。</p>"
        },
        "81": {
            "verses": {
                "56:81": {
                    "id": 81
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以物配主者啊！难道你们不信这言辞并否认它吗？</p>"
        },
        "82": {
            "verses": {
                "56:82": {
                    "id": 82
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对赐予你们给养和诸多恩惠的真主，你们以否认替代感谢，把雨水的降下归于预言，故你们说：“我们因这个预约或那个预言而获得了雨水。”</p>"
        },
        "83": {
            "verses": {
                "56:83": {
                    "id": 83
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当灵魂到达喉咙的时候，</p>"
        },
        "84": {
            "verses": {
                "56:84": {
                    "id": 84
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那时，你们看着面前濒死之人，</p>"
        },
        "85": {
            "verses": {
                "56:85": {
                    "id": 85
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我的知识和大能，以及众天使比你们更接近他，然而，你们看不见天使。</p>"
        },
        "86": {
            "verses": {
                "56:86": {
                    "id": 86
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>假若如你们所佯称的，你们不会被复生，也不会依据你们的行为而被报酬的话，</p>"
        },
        "87": {
            "verses": {
                "56:87": {
                    "id": 87
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那么，如果你们是诚实者，怎么不将从死者身体出来的灵魂返回躯体呢？你们绝无能力那样做！</p>"
        },
        "88": {
            "verses": {
                "56:88": {
                    "id": 88
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>如果死者是争先行善者，</p>"
        },
        "89": {
            "verses": {
                "56:89": {
                    "id": 89
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他将享有不再劳累的轻松、美好的给养和享受一切心中所欲的乐园；</p>"
        },
        "90": {
            "verses": {
                "56:90": {
                    "id": 90
                }
